  ($c$fix-the-email-validator$c$, $c$Fix the Email Validator$c$, $c$The function `isValidEmail(email)` should return true if the email has exactly one '@', a non-empty local part, a non-empty domain with at least one dot, and a TLD of at least 2 characters. It has 2 bugs.

