Each tile shows: a small icon emoji or symbol at the top (e.g. ⚡, 🔥, ★), a large bold stat number (e.g. '1,284', '98%', '4.9'), and a muted label below (e.g. 'Requests', 'Uptime', 'Rating').
The three tiles sit in a horizontal flex row with ~16px gap.
Stat numbers should be white and at least 28px. Labels should be muted (#9ca3af), font-size ~13px.
HTML and CSS only — no JavaScript.$c$, $c$clone_battle$c$, $c$css_battle$c$, $c$medium$c$, 20, $c$html$c$, $c$<!DOCTYPE html>
