  ($c$pricing-page-speed-build$c$, $c$Build a SaaS Pricing Page$c$, $c$Build and deploy a responsive pricing page for a fictional SaaS product.
Include three tiers (Free, Pro, Enterprise) each with a name, monthly price, a short tagline, a bulleted feature list (4-6 items), and a CTA button.
Highlight the recommended 'Pro' tier visually (e.g. border, badge, or elevated card).
