Include a sticky header with a logo and nav links, and a footer with social links.
Aim for a Lighthouse accessibility score above 85 — all images must have alt text and interactive elements must be keyboard-accessible.$c$, $c$speed_build$c$, $c$url_submit$c$, $c$easy$c$, 25, $c$javascript$c$, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, false),
